findings.title: Owner can add addresses in dividend lock list
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to add addresses in the dividend lock list without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can change dividendLockEnabled and dividendLockInterval
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify critical contract settings, potentially leading to unintended behavior or security risks.

findings.title: Owner can enable/disable transferLockEnabled
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to enable or disable the transfer lock feature.

findings.title: Owner can change master of the contract
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the master of the contract, which may lead to unauthorized changes and potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change contract pair
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the contract pair.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the dividends
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses from receiving dividends.

findings.title: Owner can change distribution criteria
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the distribution criteria of the contract.

findings.title: Owner can change gas for processing
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the privilege to modify the gas used for processing.

findings.title: Owner can finish initial distribution (allows transfers)
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to finish the initial distribution, which allows token transfers.

findings.title: Owner can include in allowed to transfer list
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to include addresses in the allowed to transfer list, which may lead to unauthorized access or manipulation.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from transfer, maxWallet and fee restrictions
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses from transfer, maxWallet, and fee restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can change maxWallet amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maxWallet amount, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change swapBack settings
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify swapBack settings, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change target liquidity
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the target liquidity, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change fees and fee receivers addresses
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify fees and fee receiver addresses, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract tokens and BNBs
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw contract tokens and BNBs without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can multisend token amounts
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the privilege to send multiple token amounts.

findings.title: Master address can rebase
findings.description: The master address has the privilege to rebase, which may lead to unintended consequences or security risks.

findings.title: Arithmetic accuracy
findings.description: Rounding errors due to division before multiplication.
